code: public static DataSet<Edge<Long, NullValue>> getDefaultEdgeDataSet(ExecutionEnvironment env) {     List<Edge<Long, NullValue>> edgeList = new LinkedList<>().     for (Object[] edge : DEFAULT_EDGES) {         edgeList.add(new Edge<>((long) edge[0], (long) edge[1], NullValue.getInstance())).     }     return env.fromCollection(edgeList). }
